document.discussion_title: Mouser Electronics Continues Hall of Fame Sponsorship at FIRST Championship Event
document.topic_text: Mouser Electronics Continues Hall of Fame Sponsorship at FIRST Championship Event Monday, 25 April 2016 ( 43 minutes ago ) ST. LOUIS--(BUSINESS WIRE)--#EmpoweringInnovationTogether--Mouser Electronics is a major sponsor of the FIRST Championship April 27-30 in St. Louis. The robotics event, which fosters STEM education, will attract thousands of students from around the world.
